		<outline title="<![CDATA[Chatterbox Audio Theater]]>" xmlUrl="http://www.chatterboxtheater.org/chatterbox-feed.rss" type="rss" text="<![CDATA[Chatterbox Audio Theater]]>" htmlUrl="http://www.chatterboxtheater.org" description="<![CDATA[Chatterbox creates fully soundscaped audio works for free download. With rare exceptions, Chatterbox shows are recorded live, with manual sound effects and as little post-production editing as possible.]]>" />
